Class NewTempSensorAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • itec3030.assignments.a2.NewTempSensorAdapter

  • public class NewTempSensorAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is an adapter that adapts SSDCS function calls into ones interpretable by the new sensors that were developed under the observer design principle
